<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Xgs_pic_ss_01.jpg" class="image" title="The XGS PIC 16-Bit game development board"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e9/Xgs_pic_ss_01.jpg/180px-Xgs_pic_ss_01.jpg" width="180" height="179" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
