<li><a href="http://www.gamedev.net/" class="external text" title="http://www.gamedev.net/" rel="nofollow">GameDev.net</a>, a leading resource for game development</li>
<li><a href="http://www.devmaster.net/" class="external text" title="http://www.devmaster.net/" rel="nofollow">DevMaster.net</a>, a game development resource</li>
</ul>
